{"lastModified":1768914630991,"uri":"c::32018258056::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nOur Catamaran Bali 4.6 “Brain” is a sleek and stylish sailing vessel that is perfect for exploring the crystal-clear waters of Croatia. This luxurious catamaran is designed to provide maximum comfort and space for its guests, making it the ideal choice for a family vacation or a group of friends looking to experience the beauty of the Adriatic Sea.\n\nOne of the most striking features of the Bali 4.6 is its spacious and airy design. The catamaran’s wide beam of 7.66 meters and generous length of 14.28 meters (46 ft) provide a feeling of openness and freedom, while the large panoramic windows and open-plan layout fill the interior with natural light. The main salon and cockpit are seamlessly connected, creating an inviting indoor-outdoor living space — perfect for enjoying meals, relaxing, and socializing with family and friends.\n\nThe Bali 4.6 offers four elegant double cabins and an additional fifth cabin with bunk beds, comfortably accommodating up to 8 + 1 guests. Each cabin has been thoughtfully designed to ensure privacy and relaxation, featuring ample storage, natural lighting, and three private bathrooms.\n\nPowered by 2 Yanmar engines of 57 HP each (2 × 41.92 kW), this catamaran offers smooth and reliable performance on the water. The classic mainsail and self-tacking jib make it easy to sail even for those with less experience, while the steering wheel system ensures excellent control and maneuverability. With a fuel tank capacity of 800 liters and a water tank of 860 liters, Bali 4.6 is ready for extended voyages across the Adriatic.\n\nBuilt in 2024 by the renowned Catana Group, the Bali 4.6 “Brain” combines innovation, comfort, and safety. With a maximum capacity of 9 registered passengers, it is perfectly suited for exploring Croatia’s picturesque islands, hidden coves, and tranquil bays.\n\nThe Bali 4.6 “Brain” is more than just a yacht — it’s a floating home that brings you closer to the sea in ultimate style and comfort. With its modern design, luxurious interiors, and advanced sailing equipment, this catamaran promises an unforgettable experience sailing the Adriatic coast.","blueprint":{"name":"BRAIN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca80d7f0-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca82fad0-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca7f2a40-ca3e-11f0-baae-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca83e530-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca819b40-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca84cf90-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca8544c0-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca7e8e00-ca3e-11f0-baae-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca7f0330-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca845a60-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca837001-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::assets::ca848170-ca3e-11f0-baaf-0355cdc63239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::161a02d0-ca3b-11f0-94c5-bb51d96953f9::